sequenceDiagram
    participant MM as ModelMesh<br/>(modelmesh-serving)
    participant Puller as model-serving-puller<br/>8084/TCP gRPC
    participant Storage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant Adapter as Runtime Adapter<br/>8085/TCP gRPC
    participant Runtime as Model Runtime<br/>(Triton/MLServer/OVMS/TorchServe)
    participant Client as External Client

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 1: Model Loading (Puller → Adapter → Runtime)

    MM->>Puller: LoadModel(modelId, modelPath, modelType)<br/>gRPC :8084 | plaintext | no auth
    activate Puller

    Note over Puller: Parse storage config from<br/>/storage-config/{key}<br/>(K8s Secret volume mount)

    Puller->>Storage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS :443 | TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: AWS IAM / GCP SA JWT /<br/>Azure SP / Custom Headers
    activate Storage
    Storage-->>Puller: Model files (binary stream)
    deactivate Storage

    Note over Puller: Write to /models/_anon_ibm_cos/{modelId}/<br/>Decompress .tar/.tgz/.zip if needed

    Puller->>Adapter: LoadModel(modelId, localPath, modelType)<br/>gRPC :8085 | plaintext | no auth
    activate Adapter

    Note over Adapter: Adapt model layout:<br/>Triton: config.pbtxt + version dirs<br/>MLServer: model-settings.json<br/>OVMS: numeric version dirs<br/>TorchServe: .mar symlinks

    alt Triton Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC :8001 | plaintext
    else MLServer Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelLoad(modelName)<br/>gRPC :8001 | plaintext
    else OVMS Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload<br/>HTTP :8001 | plaintext
    else TorchServe Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RegisterModel(url, modelName)<br/>gRPC :7071 | plaintext
    end
    activate Runtime

    Runtime-->>Adapter: Load success / failure
    deactivate Runtime
    Adapter-->>Puller: LoadModel response (success/failure)
    deactivate Adapter
    Puller-->>MM: LoadModel response<br/>gRPC | plaintext
    deactivate Puller

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 2: Inference Request (bypasses adapter)

    Client->>MM: Inference request<br/>gRPC | varies
    activate MM
    MM->>Runtime: Forward to loaded model<br/>gRPC/HTTP | plaintext | localhost
    activate Runtime
    Runtime-->>MM: Prediction result
    deactivate Runtime
    MM-->>Client: Inference response
    deactivate MM

    Note over Client,Runtime: Note: Runtime adapter is NOT in the inference path.<br/>It only handles model lifecycle (load/unload/status).

    Note over MM,Runtime: Flow 3: Model Unloading

    MM->>Puller: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC :8084 | plaintext
    activate Puller
    Puller->>Adapter: UnloadModel(modelId)<br/>gRPC :8085 | plaintext
    activate Adapter

    alt Triton Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelUnload(modelName)<br/>gRPC :8001
    else MLServer Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: RepositoryModelUnload(modelName)<br/>gRPC :8001
    else OVMS Adapter
        Note over Adapter: Batch unload (3s wait)<br/>then POST /v1/config/reload
        Adapter->>Runtime: POST /v1/config/reload<br/>HTTP :8001
    else TorchServe Adapter
        Adapter->>Runtime: UnregisterModel(modelName)<br/>gRPC :7071
    end

    Runtime-->>Adapter: Unload complete
    deactivate Adapter

    Note over Puller: Delete model files from<br/>/models/{modelId}/

    Puller-->>MM: UnloadModel response
    deactivate Puller
